Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.51,0:22:45.64,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}那彩虹的彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.64,0:22:48.47,ED-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)}我想试着去看看
